Command to find 

dmidecode -t1
  it shows vmware strings if VM
  it shows H/W details if physical
  
  example:
  
  VM:
  ===
  System Information
	Manufacturer: VMware, Inc.
	Product Name: VMware Virtual Platform
	Version: None
  
  Physical:
  ========
  System Information
	Manufacturer: HP
	Product Name: ProLiant DL385 G7
	Version: Not Specified
